description: This brave crew of firefighters has taken on a hot new challenge: blazing up the grill and serving delicious BBQ, Burgers, Wings, and lots of other favorite American classics, right out of their crazy cool fire truck turned food truck. Firehouse Grilling Co. is kindling the hearts and appetites of Cleveland with their amazing food, exciting catering services, and active involvement in the local community.So if you’re planning a party or you’re just plain ready to eat, Firehouse Grilling Co. is definitely the way to go!
name: Firehouse Grilling Co.
